  "title": "Path of the Eldar Omnibus",
  "synopsis": "The complete Path of the Eldar trilogy in one volume. On the craftworld Alaitoc, three friends each walk a different road: Korlandril the sculptor who becomes a Striking Scorpion, Thirianna the poet who trains as a farseer, and Aradryan the outcast who flees to live among rangers and corsairs. The three novels — Path of the Warrior, Path of the Seer and Path of the Outcast — retell the same gathering catastrophe from each of their viewpoints, building a portrait of a proud and ancient people, the discipline that holds them together, and the choices that bring war to their home.",
